data.description: Step inside your new home! Cozy 4 bed and 2 bath home with separate kitchen and dining room, hardwood floors, spacious pantry and enclosed rear porch. Finished second floor with room for 2 bedrooms and large common area. Full partially finished basement with living room, full bath and laundry room. Spacious yard to start your garden, cook out or just relax and enjoy the outdoor. 2 car garage with front and rear door access.
